ernal launch capacity to its own Connectivity and AI segments rather than selling it to third parties.\n*   **Government / Starshield:** While "Starshield" is not named as an isolated financial line item in these tables, government revenues are explicitly tracked under **Enterprise & Government** (which generated $1.1 billion in Q1 2026 and $4.17 billion in FY 2025) and through government contracts within **Launch & Development**.',
